---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Bacon-Eggplant Veggie Toss with Honey-Balsamic Dressing
description: A golden crumbed chicken schnitzel is too good to be messed with, so we’re keeping it simple today. All we need is a fun veggie side for the perfect pairing and we think we’ve nailed this one! Toss together roasted eggplant, potato, tomato and onion for the ultimate accompaniment to balance out all that crunchy golden goodness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
